short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Amazon Connect Service and Microsoft Teams Integrations

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Amazon Connect MS Teams Integration is a powerful extension that allows businesses to seamlessly integrate their Amazon Connect contact center with Microsoft Teams. With this integration, agents can make, transfer or conference calls directly from the Amazon Connect interface to MS Teams, allowing for more efficient communication and collaboration.
